          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
<!-- SERVICES -->
    <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
    <section id="how" class="section tint sep-top">
      <div class="wrap">
        <h2>How it works</h2>
        <div class="how-grid">
          <div class="how-step">
            <img src="assets/images/ic-chat.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true">
            <h3>1) Message me</h3>
            <p>WhatsApp or email with your address, bundle, and any notes (e.g. mower available).</p>
          </div>
          <div class="how-step">
            <img src="assets/images/ic-calendar.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true">
            <h3>2) Pick a slot</h3>
            <p>I’ll reply with available times — you choose what suits you. No long-term contract.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="how-step">
            <img src="assets/images/ic-sparkle.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true">
            <h3>3) Tidy & done</h3>
