          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
<section id="services" class="section">
      <div class="wrap">
        <h2>Services & Prices</h2>
        <div class="grid">
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Quick Refresh <span class="price">£25</span></h3>
            <p>Light weeding, sweep patio/paths, waste bagged neatly.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Garden Tidy <span class="price">£45</span></h3>
            <p>Weeding across beds, lawn mowing (your mower), tidy & sweep.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Seasonal Reset <span class="price">£65</span></h3>
            <p>~3 hours: weeding, mowing, leaf clear, patio sweep. Planting if you provide bulbs/soil.</p>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="rules">
          <h4>Good to know</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Homes with gardens only (no flats).</li>
            <li>You provide mower/plants/soil if needed.</li>
            <li>Waste is bagged for your council collection.</li>
            <li>No hedge trimming, tree work or landscaping.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

            <!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
    <section id="testimonials" class="section alt">
      <div class="wrap">
        <h2>Reviews</h2>
        <p style="opacity:.8;margin:-4px 0 14px">No public reviews yet. If I’ve worked on your garden, please leave one below — thanks!</p>

        <form class="review-form" onsubmit="return sendReviewMail(event)" aria-label="Leave a review">
          <div class="rf-grid">
            <label> Name
              <input name="r_name" type="text" required placeholder="Your name">
            </label>

            <label> Area (optional)
              <input name="r_area" type="text" placeholder="e.g. St Dunstan’s">
            </label>

            <label> Rating
              <select name="r_rating" required>
                <option value="" disabled selected>Select…</option>
                <option>5 / 5</option>
                <option>4 / 5</option>
                <option>3 / 5</option>
                <option>2 / 5</option>
                <option>1 / 5</option>
              </select>
            </label>
          </div>

          <label> Your review
            <textarea name="r_text" rows="5" required placeholder="What did you think of the work?"></textarea>
          </label>

          <label class="rf-consent">
            <input type="checkbox" name="r_consent">
            I’m happy for this review (first name + area) to be shown on the website.
          </label>

          <button class="btn primary" type="submit">Send Review via Email</button>
          <p class="rf-note">This opens your email app with the review pre-filled to <a href="mailto:waightsgardencare@gmail.com">waightsgardencare@gmail.com</a>.</p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>

            <!-- ABOUT -->
    <section id="about" class="section alt">
      <div class="wrap about">
        <div>
          <h2>About</h2>
          <p>Hi, I’m Alex. I keep garden care simple: reliable tidy-ups and clear pricing. I work flexibly around uni and message you with available slots before each visit.</p>
          <p>No faff or upsell — just the basics done well: weeding, mowing (your mower), light clears and tidy-downs.</p>
        </div>
        <figure class="img-card">
          <img src="assets/images/garden1.jpg" loading="lazy" alt="Neat flowerbed and tidy patio after a refresh">
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section id="faq" class="section alt">
      <div class="wrap">
        <h2>FAQs</h2>
        <div class="faq">
          <details><summary>Do you take garden waste away?</summary><p>No. I bag it neatly for your council collection.</p></details>
          <details><summary>Do you bring tools?</summary><p>I bring hand tools. For mowing I use your mower.</p></details>
          <details><summary>Do you work on flats?</summary><p>No — homes with gardens only.</p></details>
          <details><summary>Can I get a regular slot?</summary><p>Bookings are flexible; I confirm available times before each visit.</p></details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- BOOK -->
    <section id="book" class="section">
      <div class="wrap">
        <h2>Book a Visit</h2>
        <p>Message me directly or send a quick email request.</p>
        <div class="contact-buttons">
          <a class="btn whats" href="https://wa.me/447353738448" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp: 07353&nbsp;738448</a>
          <a class="btn outline" href="mailto:waightsgardencare@gmail.com?subject=Estimate%20request%20%E2%80%94%20Waights%20Garden%20Care&body=Hi%20Alex%2C%0A%0AI%E2%80%99d%20like%20an%20estimate.%0A%0AName%3A%0AAddress%20%28with%20postcode%29%3A%0ABundle%3A%20Quick%20Refresh%20%2F%20Garden%20Tidy%20%2F%20Seasonal%20Reset%0ALawn%20mower%20available%3A%20Yes%2FNo%0AGarden%20condition%20%28brief%29%3A%0APreferred%20days%2Ftimes%3A%0A%0AThanks%21">Request estimate</a>
          <a class="btn email" href="mailto:waightsgardencare@gmail.com">Email: waightsgardencare@gmail.com</a>
        </div>

        <form class="request" onsubmit="return sendMailto(event)" aria-label="Booking request form">
          <label>Name <input required name="name" type="text" placeholder="Your name"></label>
          <label>Address (with postcode) <input required name="address" type="text" placeholder="e.g. 12 Garden Rd, CT1…"></label>
          <label>Contact (email or WhatsApp) <input required name="contact" type="text" placeholder="e.g. you@example.com or 07…"></label>
          <label>Choose a bundle
            <select name="bundle">
              <option>Quick Refresh — £25</option>
              <option>Garden Tidy — £45</option>
              <option>Seasonal Reset — £65</option>
            </select>
          </label>
          <label>Preferred days/times <input name="times" type="text" placeholder="e.g. Sat AM, Sun PM"></label>
          <label>Notes <textarea name="notes" rows="4" placeholder="Mower available? Garden condition?"></textarea></label>
          <button class="btn primary" type="submit">Send request via Email</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CONTACT -->
    <section id="contact" class="section">
      <div class="wrap contact-box">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:waightsgardencare@gmail.com">waightsgardencare@gmail.com</a></p>
        <p><strong>WhatsApp / Phone:</strong> <a href="https://wa.me/447353738448" target="_blank" rel="noopener">07353 738448</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>
